room_title: Escape room "Ole Pappy's Trapper Cabin" by NW Escape on Wheels in Bend
room_description: A unique take on the traditional escape rooms, Ole Pappy's Trapper Cabin can come to your business or private party. Give your guests something truly unique and memorable for your event this year. Up-cycled from a 1974 camp trailer, everything except the plywood, insulation and wiring has been re-claimed and hand built by the owner and operator.
